sentences: He has worked as sound engineer and/or sound designer for films across the country including Rituparno Ghosh's Raincoat (2004).

He proved his commitment and sound perspective in Tamil and Malayalam films Other films include Veettilekkulla Vazhi (2011),Kismath (2018), Kaadu Pookkunna Neram (2016), Rakshadhikari Baiju Oppu (2017) and Eeda (2018).
